text: This is the BBC. This podcast is supported by advertising outside the UK. This Leicester Dolokyo from BBC Radio Nengale. This is Leicester Dolokgyunsich from BBC Radio Nongale. In this is Leicester Dolok Gunesich, Lear O'er in MacGelae, this Leitcher, M. 1,03, I'm a geesee Goof M.E.M. Donaldson, and in the Learer, E. Wondrings in the Western Highlands and Islands. On the leoor, had a job of a hooky to Yule in the Biawum, and there's animal, realean. year yule in the bian, and there enamel, realine. Bessan one Makhunich, and in the other than skionach. Hucka Gleor Jigunia to the Chulian and shlickachan. And it's the hook Enem to Skour Fichinich in Chowin'iwion. Galaf Donaldson in chouart Couthery Ian, Makhannich, Grunthuson. In this there was law, fat, d'erive a shulikik Gourike, and in Clotach Lough-Sgavik, and, eras, in each of Lickachan. In Tours Chahat Shachat on Lough Skavik, and, eras, in Likachan. On the Tours, chahat, on Lachach, Ereveil, on the Mapikin, Lach of the Brushwood. There's the Dule that Lachna Cray-, a figure, and Screev Donaldson, Lachna Creevick. I'd tell him a machinj, J. Hanna's Muncher in Atearish. He was Yerev in Dutter, to do brashwood, a leor of farce, in the lochah, in lawhah, in the lawmah, in Lough, Econaumet. Scrieve Donaldson Coutiach a few ruttainach a hugh-ean much-connichlea when it was a-couchach in that. Be a cheatrude to facket da eulik that was a ruach Yular Vara. The Rear Donaldson was the Yulah Mare. In Rear Donaldson, the Yulahen the Nettachach Lash, bein-chast Laivry Blavin. The Houtarison the Kingigain no one Ollaran Aalopah, in the Niche on the Sh of Lain. It's in the Tost a year a niravie on the six-gotan. Sule a year Yular Vuea a chuniki sheach Yular-Vara. It's Kaur-Inty Eatertonlson and Ean Makh Kynich in that that line, in Lashin. Heins Ean ye, that Rofioon Aun Le Kinge, and one mackunich in that in that line that one of the law that one ye that the rothioan awn lear when heikug nathar fash at the curate to the cah and gamaarag well in cullas of hean root in the chororce of that. Sule in the R. Chonich in Taring Ashty. Aouns in Learichie Wondering in the Western Highlands and Islands, and Donaldson at Tost in Leavittar, from no one skionach, Gullochael, and it'll tellull in the Gleon Illick. If one of the line of week for the Dune Enimal, he'll Lach Beekown in a week of next. I've found I've seen Gondon Schill to a chushka who chained she on the Lach and has Donaldson he came she in Skiolgain as a chouliya to be in the Finister Heanach Aach Nuch, Aach Bria, that you've in Loughah Heanichee of a votach Glick a big of Kirst Gilaur, in the Qurrae in Chach Gwfem. Hust, the botach, Gumbiag, not bianchagee but yeamagee a shieh-nog-puloch if it'd all in the moun in it. Moshin'an graan Grain in a year. Raine in Chach Uper Gah Guthier. But, Lava, this, Lame Ian Irvun. Gullav Jo Hound in here. Lehmé Donushka, to one haste to one. Charnachach Skial Tullig at Ean Boch and there's a Skaven a lot of the flute Aounson Lough
